1
00:01:03,940 --> 00:01:04,700
Xia Mu!

2
00:01:53,020 --> 00:01:55,750
[Adapted from the novel
Sweet Sixteen by Zi Yue]

3
00:01:55,750 --> 00:01:59,020
[Sweet Sixteen]

4
00:01:59,070 --> 00:02:02,060
[Episode 1]

5
00:02:02,770 --> 00:02:06,570
[Three months ago]

6
00:02:20,860 --> 00:02:21,860
Are you done?

7
00:02:22,100 --> 00:02:23,100
[Xia Mu, the Shu Family's adopted son]

8
00:02:23,100 --> 00:02:24,100
Not yet?

9
00:02:25,820 --> 00:02:26,940
Are you going back to school today?

10
00:02:28,660 --> 00:02:28,980
Yes.

11
00:02:29,660 --> 00:02:30,620
I have a class tomorrow morning.

12
00:02:30,620 --> 00:02:31,500
I'm going back soon.

13
00:02:32,620 --> 00:02:34,740
[Shu Yawang, the eldest daughter]
Why is it taking so long? Let me see.

14
00:02:35,300 --> 00:02:36,140
I'm... almost done.

15
00:02:37,140 --> 00:02:38,620
You must have drawn me poorly!

16
00:02:38,620 --> 00:02:39,940
Did you create something unflattering?

17
00:02:39,940 --> 00:02:40,540
No!

18
00:02:40,820 --> 00:02:41,620
I'm not done.

19
00:02:41,620 --> 00:02:42,700
- Three!
- I'll let you see it when I'm done.

20
00:02:42,820 --> 00:02:43,420
Two!

21
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:44,300
One!

22
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:45,620
Let me take a look!

23
00:02:46,780 --> 00:02:47,860
Fine, Xia Mu.

24
00:02:48,820 --> 00:02:49,620
Just one look.

25
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:52,540
There.

26
00:02:53,060 --> 00:02:54,100
You're doing this on purpose, right?

27
00:02:54,100 --> 00:02:54,700
No.

28
00:02:55,260 --> 00:02:56,020
Then draw it yourself!

29
00:02:56,380 --> 00:02:57,380
Next time, draw someone else!

30
00:02:57,580 --> 00:02:58,620
You're not my brother anymore!

31
00:03:00,260 --> 00:03:01,060
I'm going to look for Xiaotian.

32
00:03:03,260 --> 00:03:04,060
Seriously? You're angry?

33
00:03:05,470 --> 00:03:07,220
[Tang Xiaotian, Shu Yawang's boyfriend]

34
00:03:11,660 --> 00:03:14,100
This court has always been
the Engineering Department's!

35
00:03:14,100 --> 00:03:15,540
After four years in university,

36
00:03:15,540 --> 00:03:17,700
I've never heard of a basketball court
belonging to anyone!

37
00:03:17,700 --> 00:03:18,540
Stop!

38
00:03:18,900 --> 00:03:20,740
Let's compete for the court like men!

39
00:03:20,740 --> 00:03:21,220
Alright?

40
00:03:21,220 --> 00:03:21,940
How are going to compete?

41
00:03:22,260 --> 00:03:22,820
Shooting!

42
00:03:23,060 --> 00:03:23,700
Who is that?

43
00:03:25,180 --> 00:03:25,820
Why?

44
00:03:26,380 --> 00:03:27,140
You don't dare?

45
00:03:27,140 --> 00:03:28,180
Yawang!

46
00:03:28,180 --> 00:03:30,060
Yawang is here!

47
00:03:30,060 --> 00:03:30,860
Stop! Stop!

48
00:03:31,380 --> 00:03:32,140
Bring it on!

49
00:03:51,860 --> 00:03:52,620
Nice!

50
00:03:52,820 --> 00:03:53,580
Your turn.

51
00:03:54,380 --> 00:03:54,900
It's fine.

52
00:03:54,900 --> 00:03:55,580
We're all friends.

53
00:03:55,820 --> 00:03:56,500
Don't be angry.

54
00:03:56,740 --> 00:03:57,700
How about we use this court together

55
00:03:57,700 --> 00:03:58,540
and have a game together?

56
00:03:58,860 --> 00:03:59,700
Tang Xiaotian!

57
00:04:02,260 --> 00:04:03,620
Let's just play one game together.

58
00:04:03,620 --> 00:04:05,020
It's fine.

59
00:04:06,340 --> 00:04:06,980
Let's play together.

60
00:04:07,220 --> 00:04:08,140
Five against four?

61
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:09,020
And?

62
00:04:09,140 --> 00:04:10,820
We can still beat you.

63
00:04:11,420 --> 00:04:12,700
I'm not playing because

64
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:13,900
I'd be taking advantage of you.

65
00:04:14,340 --> 00:04:14,860
Xia Mu.

66
00:04:15,940 --> 00:04:17,740
Let my brother play with you.

67
00:04:21,740 --> 00:04:22,220
Sir!

68
00:04:22,220 --> 00:04:22,700
Coming!

69
00:04:23,620 --> 00:04:24,380
Give us...

70
00:04:24,780 --> 00:04:26,060
three mango milk puddings.

71
00:04:26,780 --> 00:04:28,300
Xia Mu is allergic to mango.

72
00:04:28,540 --> 00:04:29,900
How about this your usual?

73
00:04:29,900 --> 00:04:31,060
Two mango milk puddings

74
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:31,980
and one mung bean soup.

75
00:04:32,180 --> 00:04:32,820
Yes!

76
00:04:32,820 --> 00:04:33,340
Okay.

77
00:04:33,340 --> 00:04:33,820
Right away.

78
00:04:34,100 --> 00:04:35,660
Me and my memory!

79
00:04:35,660 --> 00:04:36,700
I'm too tired from playing basketball.

80
00:04:36,700 --> 00:04:37,420
Don't hold it against me.

81
00:04:37,420 --> 00:04:38,580
You can even forget something like this?

82
00:04:38,580 --> 00:04:39,660
What are you thinking about all day?

83
00:04:39,860 --> 00:04:40,500
Hey...

84
00:04:40,500 --> 00:04:41,380
I have to be more mindful

85
00:04:41,380 --> 00:04:42,820
for my darling, right?

86
00:04:43,140 --> 00:04:43,660
I'm going to school.

87
00:04:44,460 --> 00:04:46,100
Remember to bring
apples for me tomorrow!

88
00:04:46,380 --> 00:04:47,380
Desserts are here!

89
00:04:49,660 --> 00:04:50,460
Thank you!

90
00:05:01,540 --> 00:05:01,980
Listen,

91
00:05:01,980 --> 00:05:04,260
I have to play basketball
at least once a day.

92
00:05:05,860 --> 00:05:07,500
Who did you learn from? Look at me!

93
00:05:09,380 --> 00:05:10,020
How was it?

94
00:05:10,580 --> 00:05:11,620
You're the best.

95
00:05:11,620 --> 00:05:12,740
I think...

96
00:05:15,260 --> 00:05:16,060
I'm home.

97
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:16,620
Oh...

98
00:05:18,220 --> 00:05:19,500
Alright, go on up.

99
00:05:19,500 --> 00:05:20,300
I'll...

100
00:05:20,740 --> 00:05:21,380
go now.

101
00:05:23,900 --> 00:05:24,660
Then...

102
00:05:24,860 --> 00:05:25,500
see you tomorrow.

103
00:05:26,500 --> 00:05:27,140
See you tomorrow.

104
00:05:31,820 --> 00:05:33,020
- See you tomorrow.
- See you tomorrow.

105
00:05:35,140 --> 00:05:36,580
Turn back!

106
00:05:38,180 --> 00:05:39,620
Call me.

107
00:05:43,020 --> 00:05:44,900
I knew you wouldn't bear
to leave me behind!

108
00:05:46,180 --> 00:05:46,860
Stop it.

109
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:47,740
Don't you like it?

110
00:05:47,940 --> 00:05:48,900
Fine, I'll go then.

111
00:05:49,540 --> 00:05:50,140
Where are you going?

112
00:06:09,700 --> 00:06:10,660
You stink.

113
00:06:10,660 --> 00:06:11,580
Go take a shower.

114
00:06:17,740 --> 00:06:18,980
Don't you like me

115
00:06:19,660 --> 00:06:21,380
when I am stinky?

116
00:06:23,140 --> 00:06:23,500
Do you like it?

117
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:24,020
You stink!

118
00:06:24,020 --> 00:06:24,500
Do you like it?

119
00:06:24,500 --> 00:06:25,940
I'm not going to shower!

120
00:06:26,700 --> 00:06:27,500
You're so annoying!

121
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:52,660
Shu Yawang.

122
00:07:14,820 --> 00:07:15,780
I'm a little sleepy.

123
00:07:15,780 --> 00:07:17,020
I'm going to bed.

124
00:07:17,260 --> 00:07:18,100
Xiaotian, you should go.

125
00:07:18,100 --> 00:07:19,020
Be careful.

126
00:07:20,740 --> 00:07:21,820
I'm going back to school too.

127
00:07:28,180 --> 00:07:28,860
Aren't you going?

128
00:07:29,700 --> 00:07:30,620
I'm going.

129
00:07:30,620 --> 00:07:31,300
Of course I am.

130
00:07:31,740 --> 00:07:32,820
Your brother-in-law
will give you a lift!

131
00:07:33,220 --> 00:07:34,420
What nonsense are you saying?

132
00:07:34,420 --> 00:07:34,980
Hey,

133
00:07:35,780 --> 00:07:36,860
even if I'm not now,

134
00:07:37,180 --> 00:07:38,180
I will be...

135
00:07:38,180 --> 00:07:38,900
Are you going or not?

136
00:07:41,060 --> 00:07:41,820
The dormitory gates are about to shut.

137
00:07:44,220 --> 00:07:44,980
I'm sorry.

138
00:07:45,100 --> 00:07:45,940
I was so preoccupied with your sister

139
00:07:45,940 --> 00:07:47,580
I didn't consider your feelings.

140
00:07:48,540 --> 00:07:48,980
Go.

141
00:07:50,660 --> 00:07:51,580
Be careful!

142
00:07:52,340 --> 00:07:52,940
Go!

143
00:07:53,540 --> 00:07:53,980
Alright!

144
00:07:53,980 --> 00:07:54,420
Xia Mu!

145
00:07:54,420 --> 00:07:54,940
Wait for me!

146
00:07:55,220 --> 00:07:55,780
Call me!

147
00:07:55,980 --> 00:07:56,500
Call me!

148
00:07:59,140 --> 00:07:59,780
Coming!

149
00:08:05,180 --> 00:08:05,740
Xia Mu,

150
00:08:06,460 --> 00:08:07,660
what are you going to do

151
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:08,820
for your sister's graduation?

152
00:08:09,020 --> 00:08:09,540
None of your business.

153
00:08:10,340 --> 00:08:11,580
What do you mean?

154
00:08:12,860 --> 00:08:13,900
Let me tell you a secret.

155
00:08:14,300 --> 00:08:16,020
I'm preparing a huge surprise

156
00:08:16,300 --> 00:08:17,580
for her graduation.

157
00:08:18,860 --> 00:08:19,460
None of my business.

158
00:08:20,460 --> 00:08:20,780
You...

159
00:08:21,660 --> 00:08:23,180
Don't cycle at night.

160
00:08:23,180 --> 00:08:23,980
It's so dangerous!

161
00:08:23,980 --> 00:08:24,860
I'll give you a lift!

162
00:08:32,340 --> 00:08:33,060
Weiran?

163
00:08:33,060 --> 00:08:34,370
[Qu Weiran]

164
00:08:38,740 --> 00:08:40,380
♪SO RE MI♪

165
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:45,860
♪I can't help thinking♪

166
00:08:46,380 --> 00:08:49,660
♪A happy or sad ending♪

167
00:08:51,140 --> 00:08:54,460
♪Is up to us♪

168
00:08:54,900 --> 00:08:58,660
♪Lovers are always forced to part♪

169
00:08:59,660 --> 00:09:02,580
♪How dramatic♪

170
00:09:03,860 --> 00:09:07,140
♪Doing my best to run to you♪

171
00:09:07,780 --> 00:09:12,820
♪And our happy ending♪

172
00:09:13,300 --> 00:09:15,620
♪If I can meet you again♪

173
00:09:15,940 --> 00:09:17,900
♪And write this story again♪

174
00:09:18,340 --> 00:09:21,860
♪I don't believe in fate♪

175
00:09:22,780 --> 00:09:25,260
♪If I can hug you again♪

176
00:09:25,700 --> 00:09:27,020
♪I don't care♪

177
00:09:27,020 --> 00:09:30,340
♪About the bitter past♪

178
00:09:30,980 --> 00:09:33,100
♪Let all our partings♪

179
00:09:33,100 --> 00:09:35,180
♪Indifference and struggles♪

180
00:09:35,180 --> 00:09:38,460
♪Return to when we met♪

181
00:09:39,100 --> 00:09:42,100
♪As the crowd disappears♪

182
00:09:42,540 --> 00:09:43,860
♪It's still you♪

183
00:09:43,860 --> 00:09:50,220
♪Watching the sunset with me♪

184
00:09:51,260 --> 00:09:53,820
♪If we start again♪

185
00:09:53,820 --> 00:09:56,300
♪Can our ending be changed?♪
